name: Hotel Maya Caribe Faranda

address.addressName: Blvd. Kukulcan KM.6, Zona Hotelera, Cancun

description: Located in Cancun (Zona Hotelera), Beach House Maya Caribe by Faranda Hotels is within a 15-minute walk of Tortuga Beach and Langosta Beach.  This beach resort is 3.8 mi (6.2 km) from La Isla Shopping Mall and 3.8 mi (6.2 km) from Cancun Interactive Aquarium.
